		   README for LLMP (Linux Lighttpd Mysql PHP)

INFOMATION
-------------------------
We have LAMP, LNMP, LANMP, why do you recreate the wheel called the LLMP?
Just for fun.

What distributions does it support? 
*Only* Debian and Ubuntu supported currently.


INSTALL
------------------------- 
gunzip -cd llmp-x.x.x.tar.gz | tar xvf -
./llmp.sh <domain> <mysql_password for root>

DOMAINS
------------------------
./domain.sh <add | rm> <domain> 

UPDATE
------------------------
./update.sh


